Global Air Purifier for Smoke Market Insights
Air Purifier for Smoke Market size was valued at USD 2.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 4.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Air Purifier for Smoke Market Overview
The global air purifier for smoke market has seen significant growth due to increasing awareness of air quality and the rising concerns over health risks from smoke pollution. In 2023, the market size was valued at approximately USD 4.5 billion and is expected to reach USD 8.5 billion by 2030, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 8.8%. This growth is driven by advancements in air filtration technology and increasing adoption by households and commercial spaces affected by smoke from wildfires, industrial pollution, and other sources.

